  <div class="story-body-section">
    <div class="story-text reveal">
      <p class="story-p">The Native Folks was born in the heart of rural India — where the rhythm of the seasons still dictates the flow of life. We believe that true nutrition isn't found in a laboratory, but in the dark, fertile soil managed by hands that have known the land for generations.</p>
